<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.9.10">
<l>kārār kaṭalai yaṭaittiṭ ṭilaṅkaipuk</l>
<l>kōrātāṉ poṉmuṭi yoṉpatō ṭoṉṟaiyum</l>
<l>nērā vavaṉtampik kēnī ḷaracīnta</l>
<l>vārā vamutaṉaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
<l rend="indent">vayōttiyar vēntaṉaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Jump and sing about the unceasing nectar who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having obstructed the black sea, entered Laṅkā,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] cutting off the one and nine golden crowns</l> 
<l rend="indent">of the ignorant one,</l>
<l>gave the vast kingdom to that one’s younger brother.</l>
<l>Jump and sing about the king of Ayodhyā!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
